The paper deals with facial image super-resolution, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses unsupervised domain adaptation (UDA) methods, which are a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves image processing techniques, which fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) subcategories.
